name: Atenciones por distrito y efector
query:
SELECT 
    CONCAT(e.distrito, ' - ', e.name) AS "Distrito y Efector:Data:250",
    COUNT(a.name) AS "Cantidad de Atenciones:Int:150"
FROM 
    `tabAnimal` an
JOIN 
    `tabAtencion` a ON a.parent = an.name
JOIN 
    `tabEfector` e ON a.efector = e.name
GROUP BY 
    e.distrito, e.name
ORDER BY 
    e.distrito, COUNT(a.name) DESC
